caption: (Translated by Google) Excellent attention, the food very yy rich, I loved the guacamole, and the xocteles waw divine I took 3 different and each one myyyy tasty  (Original) Excelente atención, la comida muyyy rica, el guacamole me encanto, y los xocteles waw divinos me tome 3 diferentes y cada uno myyyy sabrosos

I ordered a milkshake from this restaurant.  I received plain cold water with chocolate powder stirred in it. Further, it was poured in a plastic soup container. I don't know if I was more upset or shocked

Terrible experience & customer service ever! I mentioned it was my daugther's birthday. The drinks were disgusting water downed. The waitress advised us after we placed a order that they were closing however, the way she hovered over us every second was astonishing. I did not get a chance to finish my food until she said you want this to go. I did not get a chance to finish my drink & she placed the check at the table. I was appalled that a party of three she had the audacity to place an automatic gratitity. She made several mistakes moreover, the manager came and told us to leave because they were ready to leave. The food was okay but nothing grand and spectacular. I would advise for customers DO NOT EAT HERE. There are plenty of authentic Mexican restaurants that caters to their customer & are thankful for the service. My daugther did not even get a Happy Birthday Song & I was told she would.
